item.name: minecraft:leather_chestplate
item.lore: It is the traditional clothing of the Kokiri. The Kokiri Tunic does not possess any special abilities.

item.name: minecraft:leather_chestplate
item.lore: The Zora Tunic is a tunic that allows Link to breathe underwater in The Legend of Zelda: Ocarina of Time. However, You are not Link and this is not Ocarina of Time, so you will drown.

item.name: minecraft:leather_chestplate
item.lore: The Goron Tunic allows Link to survive in very hot areas through unexplained means, though it is made clear that it is, at least to a degree, fireproof. However, You are not Link, so you will burn to a crisp.

pages.page: {"text":"Minecraft has a secret. This is normal, everything and everyone has secrets, but we're not interested in those. We're interested in the Minecraft secret\n\nIt is said by those who know that this secret has changed the way that they will forever"}

{"text":"view Minecraft. It is claimed that those who discover this secret are driven into deep regret, flooded with a want, a need to forget that they ever found out.\n\nOnly the foolish and the brave, though it could be argued these are one and the same,"}

{"text":"would dare to try and purposefully find the secret behind Minecraft.\n\nHeed these warnings, turning the pages any further than this will teach you something you cannot forget. Do not think this risk trivial."}
{"text":"This is your last warning.\n\nDo not turn the page."}
{"text":"(The remaining pages are missing. There are scorch marks on the final cover, and torn remains in the gutter)"}
